| HistoryText             = The Wilders were a group of animals and unnamed citizens pulled out of New York City shelters under the pretense of compensated medical testing, but were instead subjected to horrible ghastly experiments using radioactive chemicals to replicate the incident that gave [[Matthew Murdock (Earth-616)|Daredevil]] his powers. Bullseye had them gathered and tested before setting them loose on the city to wreak havoc where the Wilders' new hypersenses would drive them into a mad frenzy. Daredevil managed to track down and incapacitate the Wilders as they rampaged across the city by using their enhanced senses against them.{{r|Daredevil Vol 3 23}}
